{"type": "article", "id": 20686, "title": "盆栽支架", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-14T07:30:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150218e0Q32ktn4wBHgshM.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是美国加州的一家工作室 NATIVE STANDARD 新推出的盆栽支架系列，有三种，都将白色的钢管扭曲成三角形，或者借助巧妙的平衡立在地上，或者钉在墙上。钢管上连接了一个圆环，可以将盆栽放在中间。白色的钢管非常纤细，看似摇摇欲坠的花盆却能稳定地立在上面，比起普通的支架多了一份活力。售价 80 美元，<a href=\"http://www.nativestandard.com/collections/collection-n-1/products/suspended-planter\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261505333OsFwRcyM154P29W.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150533Z0IfKgjElk1s5tiB.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1250\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150534Q6yMZjrRtUe8S1YF.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150534e3pFaoTHmGXPtljZ.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1250\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261505355wyRUuSaeq3fjKkJ.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1250\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}